5000|$|David [...] "Dave" [...] Sweeney is a {{prominent}} Australian anti-nuclear campaigner. He {{works for the}} Australian Conservation Foundation and acts an opinion writer and spokesperson on topics including uranium mining, nuclear waste, nuclear energy, <b>nuclear</b> weapons <b>proliferation,</b> <b>nuclear</b> accidents and related indigenous rights issues. Sweeney has made appearances in or contributed to several documentary films which include discussion of nuclear issues. He {{has been described by}} Matthews Stevens of the Australian Financial Review as [...] "one of the nation's hardest working anti-nuke campaigners." ...|$|R
