50|$|Enrichment {{technology}} is primarily {{used to create}} enriched nuclear fuel, {{but it can also}} be used to create weapons-grade nuclear material. The main goal of a fuel bank is therefore to minimize the risk of further <b>nuclear</b> weapons <b>proliferation</b> by removing the need for countries to possess enrichment technology.|$|R
